##  Baseline Scores

Scores from running `inference.py` with `Qwen/Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct` via HF Router:

| Task | Score | Steps | Status |
|------|-------|-------|--------|
| `transaction_dispute` | 0.65 | 3 |  PASS |
| `card_block` | 0.83 | 4 |  PASS |
| `loan_enquiry` | 0.70 | 5 |  PASS |
| **Average** | **0.72** | - | ** PASS** |

